Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: Computes a Linear Regression Using the Bag of Little Bootstraps Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Austin Way
Authors@R:
    person("Austin", "Way", email = "arway@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Austin Way <arway@ucdavis.edu>
Description: This package uses the Bag of Little Bootstraps Algorithm to return a list of m lists, 
    each with B different parameter estimates (sigma and coef). Calling the methods sigma(), coef(), confint(), etc. will combine the
    results into a single value or term.
